reviews.comment: Impecable job, efficient and professional. Reliable company. It’s a bit pricey but it worth it. They cleaned after they finished and my white walls remained spotless. I had 5 new outlets and a led stripe in my kitchen. Lewis, Kane and Karl did a great Job. I’ll recommend them to my  acquaintances.

Storm Electrical Solutions were excellent! Friendly service, who were easy to get hold of and book an appointment. They were able to give expert advice regarding lighting and fan choice and suggestions on positioning. The team were hard working and kept our house as clean and tidy as possible throughout the job. We would highly recommend and are delighted with the result. It has elevated the look of our house. Thank you
Karl and his team are fantastic to deal with. Proper advice, very competitive pricing and tradesman who actually cleaned up after themselves! Highly recommend.
Karl and the team did an excellent job installing new network cables in my office. Incredibly professional service and great value for money, would 100% recommend.

Karl Rainbow was exceptional. For the last 6 months, he has endlessly come to try to fix my air conditioning system, trying all avenues and options. Karl, is so approachable, so considerate, and so kind. While here, I asked him to help me out with something minor, and he automatically offered his assistance. Karl, always kept me posted with outcomes, and with processes. As he left today, he said to me...any issues with anything, don't hesitate to ask...this is service that adds value to someone's life.
I have shared with family and friends, the amazing service from Storm Electrical Solutions.

Karl and his team absolutely went above and beyond.
From the initial quote, to the installation of a new reverse cycle air conditioner.
Karl explained everything so clearly and was completely transparent with his quoting.
If you are after great old fashioned service and a great cost effective electrician look no further than Storm Electrical Solutions.
I couldn’t recommend him and his team enough.
I highly recommend Storm Electrical Solutions. They have done a few jobs for us and we are really happy with the  work completed. They are super friendly, punctual and very professional!

Karl and the team at Storm Electrical are amazing! They helped with the electrical in our kitchen reno and we couldn't be more pleased with the result.
Karl and his team are full of experience and knowledge. They were happy to answer any questions we had  and explained the process of what they were doing every step of the way.
Thanks guys, we'd be happy to use your services again and will refer friends and family for any future jobs!
Cheers
Sarah & Ryan

We had what I would consider a pretty difficult split system install over two floors in an existing 2 story home. And to complicate matters further, we had some fairly stringent requirements we needed to be met for the
install.

From the initial visit and quote, Karl listened to our requirements and then took his time exploring and then explaining to us all possibilities and options available. As soon as the job commenced, Karl and his team went above and beyond and we could not have been happier with the final outcome.

If you are after an electrician that will listen to your needs and then deliver a cost effective solution, look no further than Karl and his team at Storm Electrical. I couldn't recommend Karl and his crew enough.

I was very impressed with the professional service provided by Karl and his team from start (initial enquiry) to finish (completion of work, including cleaning up afterwards). Their communication, customer understanding and general conduct was 5 star. I don’t normally write public reviews but they really deserve great reviews.

Karl and his team are trusted experts. He came and advised about the sizing of my unit, they've implemented a new and better one (as the old was a write off) and kept it clean and neat. I live in a two storey home so having experienced professionals who will not rip you off to deliver a fantastic job is always a great thing! 👍

Karl was extremely helpful and very professional. Storm team was quick, clean, friendly and their services were very fairly priced. They did an amazing job at our place, one of the best electricians out there for sure. Definitely recommend their services for any electrical job.
Thanks again mates!

We recently had pleasure working with Karl from SES Electrical to install an additional recessed power outlet behind the TV in our home, and we couldn't be more pleased with the results. The job was done promptly, and the quality of Karl’s work exceeded our expectations. I highly recommend SES for any electrical needs – a top-notch service from start to finish. Thank you! 🙏

Top-class electricians! Karl and his team took on a major project at our house, doing complex electrical upgrades and coordinating necessary works with the energy provider. We found them to be highly professional, responsive and reliable. Lovely guys, too. I would not hesitate to recommend Storm to anyone seeking super-high quality electricians.

Karl and Dave were fantastic in providing excellent electrical work and services to us. Very professional, thorough, responsive, punctual and trustworthy. They offered very honest professional advice and with excellent work ethics. Their high quality of work and services way exceeded our expectations, and the charges were really reasonable. We would highly recommend Karl and Dave. Thank you guys and you are a great team!

Highly recommend!! After waiting over two weeks for the real estate electrician we got in touch with Karl who came straight out & had the job sorted in no time at all! Amazing team, professional, friendly & no wasting time!

Karl was prompt and professional right from the first phone call seeking a quote. He offered advice on what was possible, clearly explanation of the end outcome, clear and understandable quoting, and flawless execution. Karl takes pride in his trade and treats customers with respect and professionalism. Will be calling SES again without hesitation.

Hands down fantastic experience and service - from initial consultation and quoting process, through to the execution of work. First class work - Loving the difference even the smallest of feature additions based on Karl's recommendations have made to my home. Highly recommend Karl and his team!
Fixed our aircon during a week it was 38 degrees each day. Great service at very reasonable prices. Would not hesitate to recommend.

I had a new ceiling fan to be installed and a couple of new power point to be added in the house. SES were amazing! Karl, David and Louis came over to get the job done, they were all very professional, did an amazing job. Had to make a couple of decisions on the spot and they were very engaging and explained everything to me so that  I could make the decision that suited me the best. Highly recommend and I will definitely call them back for any future electrical needs.

Had Karl come down and look at a problem with a recently installed UPS and generator system at our factory by another company.

He identified the problem straightaway and explained clearly what it was and what was needed to rectify the problem.

I can not speak highly enough of Karl's expertise and professionalism. Got us out of a tight spot in the after hours of the day. 10/10 will use him again!

I highly recommend SES! Karl from SES installed a ceiling fan in my apartment (replacing an existing light fixture). Thank you so much for the great service, Karl.
From the get go, he was extremely professional and reliable. I would 100% use their services again.

I was ever so greatful for the honesty that Karl provided me when rewiring our house, through his knowledge and customer first attitude he saved us money and time. The team are professional, work hard and clean up after themselves!

I have recommended them to family who have also had a positive experience.

For any electrical needs you have, storm electrical solutions is who you need.

Thanks again Karl for everything!
Karl and his team were excellent to deal with, good communication from start to finish. Job completed to an excellent standard. Would recommend and will use again
Always cheerful & professional. Has done quite a few jobs for me over the years. I've been very satisfied with Karl & his team at Storm Elictrical Systems

Karl is very professional. Our cctv and lights can't work due to electrical problems. Other electrical company quotes us for 2 people with at least 4 hours to find solution. But Karl helped us solve the problem within only 20 minutes!! much thanks!

Karl and the team have always been on hand for all my electrical solutions. We have done lots of renos this year and Karl has always been professional when called upon at short notice.
We recently had a new split system installed and Karl’s knowledge saved us hundreds of dollars, being able to source great products at great prices!

Required a data switchboard to be installed in the garage and spoke to Karl. He was very easy to talk to and made things very simple. Went out of his way to fit me into his schedule and chased the best prices for me. He did an awesome job and would highly recommend!
